description: The investment seeks to provide total return. In pursuing the fund's investment objective, it will invest in exchange-traded funds ("ETFs") that primarily invest in fixed income securities, real estate investment trusts ("REITs"), master limited partnerships ("MLPs"), dividend paying equity stocks including utility stocks, and exchange-traded notes ("ETNs"). The fund may also invest in ETFs that provide the inverse of the return of high yield bonds, U.S. treasury securities, REITs, MLPs, utilities, and dividend stocks.
name: Tactical Income ETF
